lead_paragraph: If the Washington Redskins decide to place the franchise tag on quarterback Kirk Cousins, it will cost them $19.95 million for 2016 under the values agreed upon by the NFL and the players' union.

headline.print_headline: QB Franchise Tag Set at $19.95 Million
